{"tid":2166813,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇一首歌以前對你影響好深 而家聽返又另一種感受","createTime":"2020-08-20T16:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T16:21:16.000Z","uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d0f2f74656fd223223be35d8e292c528962a52","tid":2166813,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"我同ex以前一齊行 一齊去旅行 一齊訓 一齊做咩都好 都係會聽住南山南 <br />\n可以話係我地嘅定情歌之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾年每次聽都會諗起佢 一齊行嘅路 一齊去嘅旅行 一齊做嘅弱智嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以覺得呢首歌好sad 每次playlist隨機播到呢首都會避開唔聽<br />\n直到之前遇到鍾意嘅人先至放低咗少少<br />\n點知一聽返呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街忍唔到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 街頭笑到街尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明淨係睇過段片一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁我徹底忘記左我ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真非假膠"},{"pid":"c8ca029ae9d1ea5b12e24c83a062f4f7ffce9c00","tid":2166813,"uid":13458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"念念不忘<br />\n以前聽好sad<br />\n依家聽又覺得好sweet"},{"pid":"816b017f62dde54c126a9ebfec2517ccdafd33fa","tid":2166813,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8ca029ae9d1ea5b12e24c83a062f4f7ffce9c00","tid":2166813,"uid":13458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"念念不忘<br />\n以前聽好sad<br />\n依家聽又覺得好sweet"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"我聽耿耿於懷都有同樣feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}